Messages:
~~~~~~~~~
- keep lines in order (messages are called with number of line) !!!
- chars with ASCII<32 are taken as end of line => Tab is begin of comment


Outro, Totaloutro:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
@outro_begin - begin of text for outro scrolling
@totaloutro_begin - begin of text for totaloutro scrolling
@outro_end   - end of text for outro scrolling
@worlds - is substitued with line 52 or 53
@comment - is substitued with line 54 or 55

- text is centered
- sizes of scrolling: 40x100 chars
- chars with ASCII<32 are token as end of line => Tab is begin of comment


Info:
~~~~~
@begin - begin of the info-text
@next  - next page
@end   - end of the info-text

- sizes of info page: 76x32 chars
- Tabs are supported

